  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dcf\u0db1\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbb  \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dca\u0db8\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d9c\u0ddc\u0da9\u0db1\u0dd0\u0d9c\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0d9a \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A fire broke out in a four storey building in Panadura",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A fire broke out on the third floor of a four storey building in the Panadura shopping complex this afternoon (26), Panadura South Police said.",
        "The fire broke out on the third floor of a family living in the ground floor and second floor of a four storey building on Arthur We Dias Mawatha in Panadura.",
        "Police say the parents were with a small child when the fire broke out and they came out of the building and survived.",
        "Two fire engines of the Moratuwa Municipal Council were deployed to douse the blaze before it spread to nearby buildings.",
        "The cause of the fire has not been identified yet, the Moratuwa Fire Brigade said."
      ],
